and is blocked from going to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999992960511, \"rank\": 6.79629818720441e-10, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donbas\", \"score\": 0.9999217612741129, \"rank\": 7.82448477280386e-05, \"text\": \"Donbass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donbas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donbas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 844}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is just about the United States supporting the Israeli army,\\\" he noted.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999168357630711, \"rank\": 4.650435076245689e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Israeli army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is one-country control-because of the money controlling the rest of the world and determining the lives of people and athletes\\u2026 working their whole life to compete in the Olympics and then - nah, you can not go to the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one-country control\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"the lives\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"their whole life\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the biggest travesty.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest travesty\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know what else to say.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crazy,\\\" Monson added.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_S._Monson\", \"score\": 0.9999999942569957, \"rank\": 5.743044520351139e-09, \"text\": \"Monson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_S._Monson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_S._Monson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Summer Olympic Games were hosted by the French capital of Paris between July 26 and August 11.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9659320625368326, \"rank\": 0.01825982926891048, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999771966943, \"rank\":